Transmutation
Level: Sor/Wiz 0
Components: V,S
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Touch
Target: Construct touched
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes (harmless)

When laying your hands upon a construct that has at least 1 hit point remaining, you transmute its structure to repair damage it has suffered.  The spell repairs 1 point of damage.